multiple_dispatch¶

pychemengg.utils.multipledispatch.multiple_dispatch(dispatch_on=None, option='all')[source]¶

dispatch_on = “kwarg_name” dispatch_on = “kwarg_value” dispatch_on = “kwarg_type” dispatch_on = “kwarg_name_and_type” dispatch_on = “kwarg_name_and_value” option = “all” to use all member kwargs option = a partial list of kwarg members

eg: a partial list of kwarg_names:

[“thermal_condition”, “flow”, “location”, “unheated_case”]
